#tr.en: Begone Evil, evil angel, evil demon, evil poultergeist, evil ghost,
1. %n šiptu duppir lemnu šēdu lemnu utukku lemnu alû lemnu eṭemmu lemnu
BabaHel1 i 1a. [x x x x x x x] lem#-nu# u₂-tuk-ku lem-nu a-lu-u₂ lem-nu e-ṭem₂-m[u] lem-nu
$ line continues
