#tr.en: that which falls from heaven, the flash of a star, the fall of Bennu,
6. %n miqit šamê ṣereh kakkabi miqit benni
BabaHel1 i 3b. mi-qit AN-e ṣe-re-eh MUL mi#-qit {d}be-en-nu
